snippet.title: The End Is Nigh! (teaser trailer)
snippet.description:
The End is Nigh - coming to Steam july 12th 2017!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/583470/The_End_Is_Nigh/

a game by Edmund McMillen (the binding of isaac + super meat boy)
and Tyler Glaiel (Closure)
Music by Ridiculon 
Voiced by Rich Evans 
Trailer by James Id

for more info - http://edmundm.com/
